---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — Whisp"
  description="Whisp is built by Eyes Wide Wellness. We believe meaning is personal — and technology should help you find yours."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Our story</span>
      <h1>Built for the meaning-seekers</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container page-body">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-main">
        <p class="lead">
          Whisp began with a simple observation: millions of people notice signs, track synchronicities,
          and log dreams — in scattered notes, camera rolls, and memory. There was no tool that actually
          helped them make sense of it.
        </p>

        <p>
          We built Whisp because we believe in the power of personal meaning-making. Not the kind handed
          down by a generic app or a one-size-fits-all interpretation guide — but the kind that emerges
          when you pay attention to your own patterns over time.
        </p>

        <p>
          The universe, or your subconscious, or the synchronistic fabric of reality — whatever lens
          you use — is always speaking. Whisp is the journal that helps you hear it.
        </p>

        <div class="about-divider">
          <span class="divider-mark">✦</span>
        </div>

        <h2>Our philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          We don't tell you what your signs mean. We believe that meaning is irreducibly personal —
          shaped by your history, your beliefs, your cosmology. A crow means something different to
          someone raised on Norse mythology than to someone who lost a loved one last year.
        </p>
        <p>
          So Whisp's AI is belief-aware. You choose your lenses — astrology, numerology, Jungian
          psychology, spiritual traditions, or none of the above — and the app only uses frameworks
          you've opted into. Your meaning, built from your patterns.
        </p>

        <h2>About Eyes Wide Wellness</h2>
        <p>
          Whisp is made by Eyes Wide Wellness, a small studio focused on tools for inner awareness.
          We're a team of practitioners, developers, and lifelong seekers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Questions or thoughts? We'd love to hear from you:
          <a href="mailto:hello@eyeswidewellness.com" class="inline-link">hello@eyeswidewellness.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <div class="sidebar-glyph">◎</div>
          <h3>Core beliefs</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Meaning is personal, not universal</li>
            <li>Attention transforms experience</li>
            <li>Technology should serve inner life</li>
            <li>Your data belongs to you</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <div class="sidebar-glyph">◐</div>
          <h3>What we're building</h3>
          <p>A long-term companion for your inner life. The more you log, the more Whisp understands — and the more meaning you can find.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 160px 0 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--navy-border);
  }
  .page-hero .section-label { display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cream);
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .page-body { padding: 80px 0 120px; }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
  .about-main p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem !important;
    color: var(--cream) !important;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .about-main h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .about-divider {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.3;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    padding: 16px 0;
  }
  .inline-link {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .inline-link:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .about-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }
  .sidebar-card {
    background: rgba(15, 24, 48, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid var(--navy-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px;
  }
  .sidebar-glyph {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .sidebar-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .sidebar-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .sidebar-card li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .sidebar-card li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .sidebar-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .about-sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
